# Find the Longest Word
For a given English sentence, find the longest English word in it.

### Input Format

The input only has one line, which is an English sentence with spaces but no punctuation marks.

### Output Format

Output the longest English word in the sentence. If there are multiple words with the same length, output the first one that appears.

### Time Limit
1000ms

### Memory Limit
262144KB

This is an incorrect code to the problem:
```c++
#include <bits/stdc++.h>
using namespace std;
int main() {
    string a,b;
    int x = 0, i = 0, max = -1;
    while(0){
            cin>>a;
            if(a==""){
                cout << b;
            }else{
                if(a.size() > max){
                  b=a; 
                  max=a.size();
                } 
            }
    }

    return 0;
}
```
### Response:
```cpp
#include <bits/stdc++.h>
using namespace std;
int main() {
    string s;
    getline(cin, s);
    int num = 0, index = 0, max = 0, maxIndex = 0;
    for(int i = 0; i < s.size(); i++){
        if(s[i] == ' '){
            num = 0;
            index = i + 1;
            continue;
        } else{
            num ++;
        }
        if(num > max){
            max = num;
            maxIndex = index;
        }
    }
    for(int i = 0; i < max; i ++){
        cout << s[maxIndex + i];
    }
    return 0;
}
```

